The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Sony, Chen champions

Hyderabad: Sony Dl Kuuncoro of Indonesia and Wang Chen of Hong Kong lifted the mens and womens singles titles, respectively in the Asian Badminton Championships at the Gachibowli Indoor Stadium here on Sunday. 

Sony defeated Kuan Beng Hong of Malaysia 15-10, 15-5 to win his third title, while former champion Chen defeated Japans Mori Kaori 11-8, 11-4 to regain the honours after 2003. 

In the mens doubles finals, the Indonesian duo of Markis Kido and Hendra Setiawan defeated Lee Jae Jin and Jung Jae sung of Korea 15-11, 15-7.The Korean pair of Lee Kyung Won and Lee Hyo Jung retained the womens doubles crown, trouncing Ogura Kumako and Shiota Reiko 15-13, 8-15, 15-5. 

Sudek Prapakarnol and Sarajee of Thailand beat Lee Jae Jin and lee Hyo jing of Korea 15-11, 14-17, 15-10 to lift the mixed doubles title. 

